headline.print_headline: Dutch Settle on Final Squad for World Cup
headline.main: Dutch Settle on Final Squad for World Cup

lead_paragraph: Coach Louis van Gaal cut six players from his preliminary squad on Saturday as the Netherlands named their final 23-man roster for the World Cup in Brazil, just hours before a warm-up international against Ghana in Rotterdam.
